    id: "inf-amedex-0027",
    topic: "Infectious Disease",
    subtopic: "Eyelid Lesions - Chalazion",
    stem: `A 12-year-old boy is brought to your clinic with complaint of an eyelid swelling that developed one week ago. The lesion is illustrated in the following photograph. The child is otherwise healthy. Which one of the following would be the most likely diagnosis?`,
